- Ce putem face ?

534
00:39:35.801 --> 00:39:37.718
Maimuţică.
conservă-ţi aerul !

535
00:39:38.178 --> 00:39:39.304
Uită-te la mine !

536
00:39:39.846 --> 00:39:41.056
