567
00:41:33.546 --> 00:41:34.547
Opreşte-te !

568
00:41:34.630 --> 00:41:35.631
Kiri. ce faci ?

569
00:41:35.673 --> 00:41:36.674
Ce faci ?

570
00:41:40.386 --> 00:41:41.720
Ce faci ?

571
00:41:41.804 --> 00:41:42.888
Nu sunt sigură.

572
00:41:43.764 --> 00:41:44.807
Asta pare bine.

573
00:41:44.890 --> 00:41:45.891
Ce ?

574
00:41:46.976 --> 00:41:48.561
