575
00:42:01.240 --> 00:42:02.408
Lo'ak ! Lo'ak !

576
00:42:31.813 --> 00:42:34.441
Masca.
Scoate-i-o !

577
00:42:34.524 --> 00:42:36.401
- Ce ?
- Nu poate respira.

578
00:42:39.654 --> 00:42:41.323
Haide !

579
00:43:24.242 --> 00:43:25.076
Kiri.

580
00:43:25.160 --> 00:43:26.411
Kiri. Kiri.

581
00:43:27.287 --> 00:43:28.413
Kiri. Kiri.

582
00:43:29.873 --> 00:43:30.874
Lo'ak.

583
00:43:31.207 --> 00:43:32.208
nu.

584
00:43:41.760 --> 00:43:44.012
O. nu !
O. nu !

585
00:43:44.095 --> 00:43:45.556
O. nu.

586
00:43:46.682 --> 00:43:48.058
Îmi pare atât de rău !

587
00:43:49.976 --> 00:43:50.977
Îmi pare rău !

588
00:44:06.535 --> 00:44:08.204
Îmi pare atât de rău !

589
00:44:23.803 --> 00:44:25.096
Spider !

590
00:44:46.701 --> 00:44:47.952
Respir ?

591
00:44:49.121 --> 00:44:50.413
Da. Maimuţică.

592
00:44:51.373 --> 00:44:52.457
Respiri.

593
00:44:55.543 --> 00:44:56.794
Sunt mort.

594
00:44:57.712 --> 00:44:59.422
Asta e Lumea Spiritelor.

595
00:45:00.798 --> 00:45:02.509
Nu. vere.
Eşti încă aici.

596
00:45:05.178 --> 00:45:06.638
Respir aerul.

597
00:45:07.514 --> 00:45:08.515
Da.

598
00:45:09.266 --> 00:45:10.517
Respir aerul !

599
00:45:11.769 --> 00:45:12.936
Respir aerul !

600
00:45:13.604 --> 00:45:14.688
Respir aerul !

601
00:45:16.148 --> 00:45:18.066
Nu-mi mai trebuie
porcăria asta !

602
