- Copiii mei !

720
00:55:03.498 --> 00:55:04.874
Fiică. calm !

721
00:55:04.958 --> 00:55:07.335
Copiii mei.
Copiii.

722
00:55:07.418 --> 00:55:08.711
Unde ?

723
